The ladies staying under his roof from various circumstances are Estrith, a cow girl of the Hosten family, Krystanya, Jan's adoptive horse daughter, and Liedde, a Sami reindeer gal along for the ride. As well as the Nisse who owe Canute one for leaving them a bowl of porridge and a double portion of butter every day for a year.
